Ing '''Ponda''' ([[Konkani Language|Konkani]]: फोंडा/Fonde) metung yang lakanbalen o ciudad ampong metung a [[w:Municipal council|municipal council]] king distritu ning [[w:North Goa district|Pangulung Goa]] (North Goa) king [[Estadu ampong teritoriu ning India|estadu]] ning [[Goa]], [[India]]. Atiu king kalibudtan (''central'') nang dake ning India. Maki dayu yang 28 km king mauli-aslagan (''south-east'') ning Panaji, ampong 17 km king pangulu-aslagan (''north-east'') ning [[Margao]], at tungku (capitoliu o cabecera) ne ning Ponda [[w:Taluka|taluka]]. Makatuglung ya king [[Panaji]] (tungkul ning Goa) ampo ing  salapungan-dalan rilis (''railway junction'') ning [[Madgaon]]. Iti ing sentru nang pang-industria ning estadu ning Goa, at dakal ya pabrika ampong ''industrial estates''; pekamabilis yang dagul kareng lakanbalen ning Goa.        

